title: FC Dallas unveil new secondary jersey for 2017 season
text:
FC Dallas unveil new secondary jersey for 2017 season February 17, 2017 9:33PM EST Follow@ mls 
The stars are shining bright for FC Dallas' new secondary jersey. 
The team unveiled the new look on Friday, which includes 11 stars positioned in a deep blue field near the top of the front, for a unique look in MLS. 
You can get this jersey and much more over at MLSstore.com now. 
Here's the front and back look of the authentic jersey: 
This is the long-sleeved look:
